g/Qu%C3%A1-Ph%C3%B9-Th%E1%BA%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-tELME7qlQW8TvPo8qzWyxg">Quá Phù Thạch độ kỳ 2 - 過浮石渡其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Th%C3%A1nh-T%C3%B4ng/author-FSJg5-ivZkPUR1nhJkA6Fg">Lê Thánh Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%BF-D%C3%A2n/T%E1%BB%A9-Ti%C3%AAu-V%C5%A9/poem-bAUZty7kpHYXKfs8k-ISCg">Tứ Tiêu Vũ - 賜蕭瑀</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%E1%BA%BF-D%C3%A2n/author-19Y6ZR7qO5ib1Hce98JOUQ">Lý Thế Dân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81/poem-u0O8cXR7dWzz0W0RZeF-qA">Vô đề - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Th%C3%A1i-T%C3%B4ng/author-9I32ODUXRXPuHHWWFnp0IQ">Trần Thái Tông</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/V%C3%B4-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-II/poem-Vy-DL7d5-Nm_0zC_flypBg">Vô đề (II) - 無題</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BB%B1c-Hi%E1%BB%81n/author-VNhahLxtqyIrLeDASL0s9Q">Thực Hiền</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
